name: Captain Carter Shield
description: June 1943. The Nazi army marches across Europe leaving death and destruction. The allied armies band together to create a new kind of solider, a super soldier. At humanity's darkest hour, a skinny kid from Brooklyn became Captain America. After turning the tide of World War II, he made the ultimate sacrifice, restoring peace and saving this universe. But in another universe, a single choice created a whole new hero. That's the moment that created a new universe. When asked to leave the room, Margaret "Peggy" Carter chose to stay, but soon it would be her adventuring into the unknown and creating a new world.
